      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "不错，傅罗卜。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00030",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "请上城楼，我母子相见。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00031",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "阎君知道，那还得了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00032",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "行个方便罢。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00033",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "使不得。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00034",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "唵嘛呢叭咪吽。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00035",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "哎呦。哎呦。不要如此。众鬼卒，将刘氏清蒂押上都城。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00036",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘氏上台子。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00037",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "一见母亲泪眼认，怎不叫人痛在心。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00038",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "长官，将我母亲焰火去了。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00039",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "众鬼卒，将刘氏清蒂焰火去了。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00040",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "刘清蒂站都城浑身颤抖，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00041",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "罗卜，我儿，儿啊！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00042",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "回龙",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "叫一声罗卜儿细听从头：",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00043",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄正板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿本是阳世人相隔幽冥，却缘何来到了酆都城楼？我的儿到酆都城将娘搭救，看不见小娇儿我两泪交流。娘说道吃长斋恤老怜幼，竟变了那铁树开花不能保留。娘不该在佛前我就将誓盟就，娘不该在阳间打僧骂道，不济贫民，开了五荤，到如今我此幽囚。我的儿啊！",
      "text_length": 117
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00044",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖缓锣鼓〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00045",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿的父修正道跨鹤西走，为娘我被阎君地府来收。娘说道阴曹府报应无有，又谁知到了阴曹，早晚间我受的是蓬头垢面，披枷带锁，口含阴灯，等何时我才得出头。儿求佛尊将娘搭救，也不枉为娘我就盼儿在心头。",
      "text_length": 94
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00046",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿啊，今当四月初八日，阎君赴龙华大会去了。你可哀告掌关，放出都城，我母子也好相见。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00047",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "长官，将我母亲放出都城。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00048",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "阎君知道，那还了得？使不得。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00049",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "唵嘛呢叭咪吽。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00050",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "大鬼"
      ],
      "text": "哎呦，哎呦，不必如此。众鬼卒，将刘氏清蒂押出都城。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00051",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刘氏走下，出城。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00052",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "罗卜，我儿，儿啊！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00053",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "娘只说阴曹府无报应，天网恢恢有神灵。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00054",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿啊，为娘披枷带锁，如何是好？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00055",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "有佛法。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00056",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "快快使来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00057",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "是。https://scripts.xikao.com/play/140020092024-03-01",
      "text_length": 51
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00058",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "对准西方身拜定，快将枷锁离娘身。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00059",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "为娘双目不明，如何是好？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00060",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "有佛法。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00061",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "快快使来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00062",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "遵命。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00063",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "对准西方身拜定，取来了甘露水付与娘亲。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00064",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿啊，",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00065",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "数载未见娇儿面，母子们相逢泪不干。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00066",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿啊，为娘肚中饥饿，如何是好？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00067",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "目莲"
      ],
      "text": "还有佛法。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14002009_e00068",
      "play_id": "14002009",
      "scene_id": "14002009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
